race.description: Tabtouch - Have You Got The Touch Maiden
race.comment: ALMOST ARTIE (6) was quickly back on track, placing at Bunbury second up before enduring a tough run there from a wide gate without much market support. Draws inside today with Fiore engaged and finds the right race. This might be her day. SEA OF GALILEE (2) peaks and will find this easier than Ascot his last two. He had reasonable support over 1800m last time, and Faithfull's booking is a decent push for his chances. EXCEED THE BOOM (4) peaks off a solid effort at Bunbury over 1400m. He's switched to a local stable on a 14-day return and can feature with average luck from an awkward barrier. CLOSE CALL (7) made decent improvement at his third start, finding one better here from the speed. This is longer and tougher, but expect him to give a sight.
